e Krisis der europäischen Demokratie, der 1925 zeitgleich in England, den USA, Frankreich und Spanien erschienen war.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Mrz 2018) 4aAmerica. 4aAmerika. 4aDemokratie. 4aParlamentarismus. 4aParliamentarianism. 4aWeimar Republic. 4aWeimarer Republik. 4ademocracy.1 aHacke, Jens, eeditor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2015z9783110438680oZDB-23-DPH0 cEPUBz978-3-11-038076-70 cprintz978305006259440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783050095134423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783050095134.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DPHb2015